data.description:
Indulge in contemporary comfort with this renovated 696 sqft condo in the vibrant neighborhood of Andover Heights Condominium. This residence has 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom on the first floor, 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom in the basement and includes two covered parking spaces. 

The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece with new stainless-steel appliances and new countertops and hardwood floors grace every room, creating a cohesive and sophisticated ambiance. Whether you're captivated by city views or proximity to Lakeside Mall, Costco, The Mall at Partridge Creek, this condo is in a highly convenient location! Don't miss the chance to make this unit your home or a great investment property!
